## Project structure

```
src/
  Api/
    {{SolutionName}}.Api/                                ← entry point; references all *.Api modules
  Modules/
    {Name}/
      {{SolutionName}}.Modules.{Name}.Core/              ← domain, commands, queries, errors, DTOs, interfaces
      {{SolutionName}}.Modules.{Name}.Infrastructure/    ← EF DbContext, repos, migrations
      {{SolutionName}}.Modules.{Name}.Api/               ← IModule impl, endpoints
  Shared/
    {{SolutionName}}.Shared.Abstraction/                 ← Result<T>, IModule, shared errors
    {{SolutionName}}.Shared.Infrastructure/              ← EF base config, Npgsql helpers
tests/
  {{SolutionName}}.Modules.{Name}.Tests.Unit/
  {{SolutionName}}.Modules.{Name}.Tests.Integration/
```

