## Commands

```bash
dotnet build {{SolutionName}}.slnx                                 # build everything
dotnet test                                                         # run all tests
dotnet run --project src/Api/{{SolutionName}}.Api                   # start API (http://localhost:5000/scalar)
dotnet ef migrations add {Name} \
  --project src/Modules/{Name}/{{SolutionName}}.Modules.{Name}.Infrastructure \
  --startup-project src/Api/{{SolutionName}}.Api \
  --context {Name}DbContext
```
